cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.GR 

This paper deals with a computer vision problem of dynamic scene deblurring using a deep convolutional neural network. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a new large-scale dataset, which involves data collection and processing, indicating that it may also belong to cs.GR (Graphics). The paper uses a machine learning approach, which suggests that it may also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with image processing, which suggests that it may also belong to cs.MM (Multimedia).
